FBIS4-40531 "drsov117_b_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-117 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Explosion Reported at Logovaz Bank in Moscow Explosion Reported at Logovaz Bank in Moscow LD1606134194 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 1200 GMT 16 Jun 94 LD1606134194 Moscow Russian Television Network Russian BFN [Text] Twenty minutes ago an explosion occurred in the building of the House of Actors in Staryy Arbat in Moscow. The premises of the Logovaz Bank were blown up. According to unconfirmed reports, there are casualities. Now our film crew is at the scene. You will see our reportage from the scene in the evening edition.
